# Player, UI & Audio Context

You are working on player/UI/audio integration, content, prefab, or editor-state surfaces. Read these docs:

1. `docs/design/core-architecture.md` — shared patterns, project structure, event bus contracts
2. `docs/design/extensible-development-contracts.md` — UI runtime bridge and interaction workflow guardrails
3. Domain doc(s) affected by your change (for example contracts, world, inventory/economy)
4. `.agent/skills/unity-project-conventions/SKILL.md` — project conventions for scripts/assets

For local player/UI/audio runtime or test cleanup, use `.cursor/rules/player-ui-audio-runtime-local-context.mdc` instead.

Do NOT load unrelated deep domain docs unless the change explicitly crosses that boundary.
